  <brief_title>Head-neck Coordination Analysis After Minimally Invasive Surgery in the Dorsal Cervical Spine</brief_title>
  <acronym>MISDCS</acronym>
  <official_title>Comparison of Open vs Minimally Invasive Dorsal Approaches for Foraminotomy and Laminoplasty in the Cervical Spine Through Performance of Head-neck-coordination Analysis</official_title>
